<http://www.uoc.edu/knowledgeManagement/eu-medical-devices> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Ontology> .
<http://www.uoc.edu/knowledgeManagement/eu-medical-devices> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#versionIRI> <http://www.uoc.edu/knowledgeManagement/eu-medical-devices/1.0.0> .
<http://www.uoc.edu/knowledgeManagement/eu-medical-devices> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/creator> "Jesús Maceda Martinez" .
<http://www.uoc.edu/knowledgeManagement/eu-medical-devices> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "An OWL ontology for representing medical devices marketed in the European Union, including manufacturers, device types, regulatory frameworks, risk classes, known risks, incidents, affected patients and field safety corrective actions. The ontology is populated from CSV datasets and supports semantic reasoning through SWRL rules and external RDF links." .
<http://www.uoc.edu/knowledgeManagement/eu-medical-devices> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "EU Medical Devices Ontology" .
